Counter-Strike Source Map

TITLE**: fy_smash
AUTHOR**: {A}E} Mr. Who?
E-MAIL**: hacklan07@hotmail.com
WEBSITE: http://hacklan07.googlepages.com/
clan website: http://www.americaneruption.net/

FILENAME: fy_smash.zip
FILESIZE: 225 kb
DATE RELEASED: 25 May 2006

CREDITS**: Thank you to Spoom for helping with the origional idea, and to my clan members for great suggestions and tweaks!

INSTALLATION INSTRUCTIONS**: Place the ".bsp", ".txt", and ".nav" in your "C:\Program Files\Valve\Steam\SteamApps\[your steam user name here]\counter-strike source\cstrike\maps" folder (the steam folder is located under Program Files by default. your steam folder may be located elsewhere.)

DESCRIPTION**: This is a knife map with two "hidden" shotguns. This map is extremely unique as you surroundings continually change as pillars come up from the floor. The effect is truely amazing.
